Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍界大戰開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻們也很賣命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們正餓著肚子等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澤 你在幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家憋不住了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表木葉的精銳忍者們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組成了五大國有史以來的第一支忍者聯軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴血奮戰在第四次忍界大戰的戰場上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們時刻擔心著家人的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎能守護我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們同樣是戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當忍界大戰爆發之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會出現禿鷲一般的鼠輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊防禦薄弱的村子 搶奪財物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們留守人員更要團結一致…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙從來都是吃不了兜著走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是鹿丸哥哥的媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別小看我們媽媽組成的娘子軍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻姐姐的媽媽也幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會提心吊膽地跑到村裏來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 井野媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止 確實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可也該考慮一下突發的特殊情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匹敵曉的強盜們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會突然出現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我想在留守期間給大家打氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在嘀咕什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平常那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡笑 哭泣 發怒 繼續歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後用笑臉迎接老公們凱旋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能一如既往地生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧 黑眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真像惠比壽老師所言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不速之客襲擊村子的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想想沒能出征的我們是多麼無能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 早點出生就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡瀨好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 保護村子也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功名祗向馬上取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看門可沒人會嘉獎你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是爺爺 會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺是火影 肯定會趕赴沙場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否擁有火之意志呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想守護這個村子的強烈意志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才媽媽拜託我去村子東側的山裏采藥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有奇怪的忍者在森林中奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊 有一百多人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百名忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 烏冬 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說嘛 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去東邊的森林采蘑菇時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等前往戰場的人凱旋時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓他們吃上美味的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 將這美味的蘑菇燒得脆脆的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙燙燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏成了火焰般的地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是忍不住了 先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個火候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火屬性的忍者 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且相當厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子的西邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 這次換西邊了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很大很大的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨忍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨忍是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是巨大的忍者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和沒說差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在村子的東邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到東邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有操縱螺旋丸的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠使用螺旋丸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已過世的只有第四代和自來也大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著的只有鳴人大哥和我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是用腳使出螺旋丸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用腳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用腳來踢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是我 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要使出渾身解數才能用手使出螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用腳踢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是詛咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子正遭受尾獸的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾…尾獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾獸啊…尾獸再次前來襲擊村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 您是在哪兒看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東方的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是尾獸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這回的尾獸是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先整理下至今為止收集到的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子的東邊 不對 西邊也有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說村子的附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算出現了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些大嬸們也會趕跑他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著增強凝聚力才那樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到我出場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸 別再偷懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去修煉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:11:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 即將有壞人來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨忍集團趁大部隊出征 前來偷襲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口吐火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還將螺旋丸傳來傳去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還和熊一起來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人們靠不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子就由我們年輕人守護到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再擺出一副火影的架子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是第三代的孫子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 以後憑實力說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人大哥也是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校裏曾是拖後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今則是村子的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是下一任火影的不二人選
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼爹的時代已經過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場上立下的功勞才能決定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守衛村子根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以為是的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 打就打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想要守護這個村子的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有火之意志的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎能成為火影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想讓你受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我被苦無刺中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才拼命不讓自己受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼事 我都會保護村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸 去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌黃 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在這附近看見的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是在這附近看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越樹枝的忍者們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噴射火焰的火屬性忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用腳操縱螺旋丸的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾獸熊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是幻影馬戲團
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近剛從霧之國逃難至木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草木皆兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會把馬戲團給看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕 就我一個人大驚小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉丟大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸 正如你所說 那些傢伙出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那不過是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然從西邊的森林…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 渡瀨喊你過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是繼忍者 武士之後的第三勢力 力士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座村莊就由我橫綱大人收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力士是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西邊的森林裏有一大堆巨人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子的西邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很大很大的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來 只有這個情報是真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著 我這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家之主都奔赴戰場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁他們不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子的東西都歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還有這種敗類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管孩子他爸們在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我們娘子軍的火之意志來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞎扯什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓這些婆娘們見識見識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對擁有火之意志的人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裏所有的人都像家人一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要守護家人的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將村民們的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得更緊密 更強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股火之意志如果能遍佈所有村民的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論村裏發生什麼 都能否極泰來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 這就是真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤…撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真礙事 快讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是木葉丸厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就將木葉丸高高舉起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野和老公都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就吃昨天的剩菜剩飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才懶得給閑在家裏的老公做飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就將中午吃剩下的拿過來好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉丸才是我們的頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人大哥算個啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神清氣爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,請讓鳴人過去吧 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,為什麼要替他出頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,就算拳拳相抵 也無法讀懂我的內心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:22:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,最強拍檔的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,本月的禮物如上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.58,0:23:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,在明信片上注明必須事項和尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,寄往所示地址
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,將抽選40名幸運觀眾頒發獎品
